  "keyFeatures": [
    "Durable agent memory and continuity across runs",
    "Structured workspace model with runtime-owned state",
    "Agent harness boundary for pluggable execution backends",
    "MCP (Model Context Protocol) server integration",
    "Proactive / cronjob-driven autonomous agent tasks",
    "Workspace apps with lifecycle management",
    "Self-evolving skills system",
    "Electron desktop shell for local development",
    "Portable runtime deployable independently from desktop",
    "TypeScript-first SDK with generated API clients"
